Source.Name: freedink-data
Source.Summary: Free, portable and enhanced version of the Dink Smallwood game engine (game data)
Source.Description: Dink Smallwood is an adventure/role-playing game, similar to classic Zelda (2D top view), made by RTsoft. The game features the twisted adventure of young Dink Smallwood, a pig farmer who leaves his town and goes on a quest to save the world. This package contains game's data files.
